INCLUDE z_mig_bp_upload_f1.

*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
* AT SELECTION-SCREEN
*---------------------------------------------------------------------*

AT SELECTION-SCREEN ON VALUE-REQUEST FOR p_file.
  PERFORM f_file_get USING p_file .


*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
* START-OF-SELECTION
*---------------------------------------------------------------------*
START-OF-SELECTION.
  PERFORM upload     USING p_file.
  PERFORM add_partner.
  CALL SCREEN 100.

